call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Possession is correctly awarded to MIA.
Butler (MIA) legally firms up in VanVleet's (TOR) path and does not deliver any contact during the screen.
VanVleet (TOR) legally contest Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Siakam (TOR) during the rebound.
Herro (MIA) moves into VanVleet's (TOR) body and delivers contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact with Gasol (TOR) as they engage during the pick.
VanVleet (TOR) legally contest Crowder's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Gasol (TOR) off-ball and doesn't affect his ability to maintain position.
Gasol (TOR) briefly grasps and releases Adebayo's (MIA) jersey.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) by going to, but not through him on the perimeter.
Siakam (TOR) legally firms up in Herro's (MIA) path.
Dragic (MIA) is late establishing himself in a legal guarding position in VanVleet's (TOR) path prior to the start of his upward motion.
Anunoby (TOR) places two hands to Dragic's (MIA) arm and body during his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Gasol (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) initiates the contact by swiping down with his right hand, subsequently restricting Crowder's (MIA) arm and affecting his ability to defend the shot attempt.
Crowder (MIA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in VanVleet's (TOR) path.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact by sliding his arm across Butler's (MIA) body off-ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After replay review, the ruling on the floor of MIA possession is correctly overturned and TOR is awarded possession.
Crowder (MIA) commits a take foul on Gasol (TOR).
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball prior to making incidental contact with Dragic (MIA).
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
